  <brief_title>Simvastatin and Metformin Therapy in PCOS Women. Prospective Randomised Trial.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Simvastatin and Metformin on Clinical, Endocrine, Metabolic and Endothelial Function of Women With Polycystic Ovary Syndrome: Prospective Randomised Trial</official_title>
