  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare effects of statins (simvastatin) and metformin on
      clinical (menstrual cycle, excessive hair, skin problems), endocrine (androgens), metabolic
      (lipids, markers of systemic inflammation), and endothelial function parameters in women with
      polycystic ovary syndrome (PCOS).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
